vampires : los suckos this brainless , low-budget attempt to cash in on the success of john carpenter 's vampires was so foul and lame that the studios could n't even bribe one of their lap-dog `` reviewers '' to crank out a glowing review for the dvd cover . or maybe they could n't afford the kickback -- who knows ? in any case , the bad casting and inept acting had a kind of narcotic quality like an over-the-counter sleeping pill and the movie had so many plot holes that i used the dvd later to drain my spaghetti . `` john carpenter presents '' -- a piece of incredible crap ! ! its general level of radioactive badness probably made me sterile